"DDOS attack"
You accidentally leaked your ip-address and
and got DDOSed. Take 3 steps back.
Questionmark Tiles
Questionmark cards are cards that
contain a questionmark and by landing on
them, a question will pop up. By anwsering
correctly, you will gain score with which you
can buy yourself an advantage in the buy
menu. You can open the inventory by clicking
on the blue card on the bottom of the game.
In the inventory you can acces the buy menu
by clicking on the store on the top right of the
inventory.
There are multiple power-ups you can buy in
the buy menu, like take 2 steps forward.
You can choose to either save the score till
or use them immediately.
The effect of the power-ups will activate if you
use them in the inventory.
(Digital Component)
Red Tiles the red colored blocks on the game-
board, if you land on a red tile you must
follow the instructions on the red card that
pops up. All red cards contain penalties. You
will be automatically moved the amount of
blocks shown on the card. So make sure you
dont land on a red tile.
